1
00:00:10,940 --> 00:00:14,020
ظآزLove crosses every cycle
of life and deathظآز

2
00:00:14,300 --> 00:00:17,580
ظآزSo let me fall with youظآز

3
00:00:17,580 --> 00:00:20,420
ظآزAll the noise of the mortal worldظآز

4
00:00:20,420 --> 00:00:24,060
ظآزIs nothing compared to her eyesظآز

5
00:00:24,060 --> 00:00:27,180
ظآزWhoever said love itself is sinظآز

6
00:00:27,380 --> 00:00:31,020
ظآزWhen a heartbeat turns into
wind and moonlightظآز

7
00:00:31,020 --> 00:00:34,180
ظآزPainting a banquet
of endless spring bloomsظآز

8
00:00:34,620 --> 00:00:35,700
ظآزHow beautifulظآز

9
00:00:35,700 --> 00:00:38,860
=Blooms for Her=

10
00:00:38,900 --> 00:00:41,820
=Episode Six=

11
00:00:42,280 --> 00:00:45,000
Princess Anhe has arrived.

12
00:00:47,840 --> 00:00:49,280
(I'm not anyone's substitute,)

13
00:00:50,520 --> 00:00:51,880
(nor anyone's pawn.)

14
00:00:53,159 --> 00:00:54,039
(I am)

15
00:00:54,600 --> 00:00:56,280
(my own blade.)

16
00:01:16,439 --> 00:01:17,239
Princess Anhe

17
00:01:17,680 --> 00:01:19,000
would you share a drink with me?

18
00:01:19,000 --> 00:01:19,680
Your Highness...

19
00:01:19,680 --> 00:01:20,480
Princess Anhe.

20
00:01:20,599 --> 00:01:21,719
You look stunning tonight.

21
00:01:22,239 --> 00:01:22,760
Move.

22
00:01:22,760 --> 00:01:23,280
General.

23
00:01:23,280 --> 00:01:24,920
Mei Lin, I never expected you

24
00:01:24,920 --> 00:01:26,920
to make two princes
fight over you like this.

25
00:01:27,159 --> 00:01:29,879
Such tawdry wiles. Impressive.

26
00:01:32,359 --> 00:01:35,319
You dared have someone kill my deputy?

27
00:01:35,799 --> 00:01:36,760
I promise

28
00:01:37,640 --> 00:01:40,040
you'll die even worse than she did!

29
00:01:42,400 --> 00:01:44,599
General, if you have time
to pick on me here,

30
00:01:45,280 --> 00:01:48,359
why not please Prince Xuanlie instead?

31
00:01:48,439 --> 00:01:49,239
You!

32
00:01:50,280 --> 00:01:51,079
Luomei

33
00:01:52,599 --> 00:01:53,879
what are you up to now?

34
00:02:02,000 --> 00:02:02,799
Pour the wine.

35
00:02:08,759 --> 00:02:09,680
Murong Jinghe!

36
00:02:13,800 --> 00:02:14,800
Prepare to die!

37
00:02:22,080 --> 00:02:22,960
(Su Jian?)

38
00:02:43,439 --> 00:02:44,240
Why?

39
00:02:44,759 --> 00:02:45,879
Aren't you afraid of death?

40
00:02:46,800 --> 00:02:48,199
With Your Highness here

41
00:02:48,840 --> 00:02:50,080
I won't die.

42
00:02:52,800 --> 00:02:53,919
Kill him!

43
00:02:54,759 --> 00:02:55,560
Stop!

44
00:02:56,120 --> 00:02:57,400
I want him alive.

45
00:02:57,680 --> 00:02:59,039
Trying to kill me?

46
00:02:59,319 --> 00:03:01,639
I'd like to see
who's so bold to do this.

47
00:03:03,759 --> 00:03:04,800
Jian

48
00:03:04,800 --> 00:03:07,159
Prince Jinghe will surely choose me.

49
00:03:07,159 --> 00:03:08,199
You'd better be careful.

50
00:03:11,260 --> 00:03:11,960
(In Memory of Shiqi)

51
00:03:11,960 --> 00:03:12,759
(In Memory of Shiqi)
(Shiqi,)

52
00:03:13,680 --> 00:03:15,479
(Murong Jinghe killed you.)

53
00:03:15,479 --> 00:03:17,159
(I promise I'll avenge you!)

54
00:03:19,159 --> 00:03:20,560
(So you're still alive.)

55
00:03:22,360 --> 00:03:24,159
(But I hurt you with my own hands.)

56
00:03:32,719 --> 00:03:33,639
Forgive me, my lord.

57
00:03:33,879 --> 00:03:35,479
The blade was laced with poison.

58
00:03:35,560 --> 00:03:37,680
It triggered the residual poison
in her body.

59
00:03:38,000 --> 00:03:39,400
The two toxins clashed.

60
00:03:39,560 --> 00:03:40,919
It has reached her heart.

61
00:03:41,280 --> 00:03:43,719
I'm afraid there's nothing I can do.

62
00:03:45,759 --> 00:03:46,560
Get out.

63
00:03:47,039 --> 00:03:48,280
Yes, Your Highness.

64
00:03:58,159 --> 00:04:02,199
(So you admit my appearance is good?)

65
00:04:09,159 --> 00:04:09,960
Your Highness

66
00:04:10,879 --> 00:04:11,919
please have some tea.

67
00:04:13,860 --> 00:04:16,860
ظآزYou were trapped in lies
born of your own schemesظآز

68
00:04:16,860 --> 00:04:18,500
ظآزAnd fate was bound by your handsظآز

69
00:04:20,860 --> 00:04:23,560
ظآزA knot of love and hatred,
endlessly tornظآز

70
00:04:23,560 --> 00:04:25,780
ظآزI fell into the ruin you broughtظآز

71
00:04:28,759 --> 00:04:29,560
Your Highness

72
00:04:30,120 --> 00:04:31,519
have I done well?

73
00:04:36,319 --> 00:04:38,720
Why? Aren't you afraid of death?

74
00:04:39,000 --> 00:04:40,279
With Your Highness here

75
00:04:40,800 --> 00:04:42,240
I won't die.

76
00:04:44,200 --> 00:04:46,900
ظآزAmid the flames of war,
you stood upon the bladeظآز

77
00:04:47,130 --> 00:04:49,600
ظآزThis illusion of a doomed fateظآز

78
00:04:49,600 --> 00:04:53,700
ظآزI wish it could have
lasted a little longerظآز

79
00:04:53,960 --> 00:04:57,420
ظآزSo burn this dream
until nothing remainsظآز

80
00:04:57,420 --> 00:05:00,700
ظآزLet the fire bring our endingظآز

81
00:05:01,060 --> 00:05:05,200
ظآزIt rekindles the snowstorm buried
in my memoriesظآز

82
00:05:05,200 --> 00:05:07,400
ظآزA winter of lies falling once againظآز

83
00:05:07,660 --> 00:05:12,000
ظآزLet me indulge in one final longingظآز

84
00:05:12,000 --> 00:05:14,400
ظآزFor the tenderness in your eyesظآز

85
00:05:14,530 --> 00:05:17,730
ظآزOne last kiss,
lingering and bittersweetظآز

86
00:05:17,760 --> 00:05:20,300
ظآزMay we never meet again
in another lifeظآز

87
00:05:27,079 --> 00:05:28,839
Your life belongs to me.

88
00:05:29,759 --> 00:05:31,279
Without my permission

89
00:05:31,439 --> 00:05:32,639
you're not allowed to die!

90
00:06:00,680 --> 00:06:04,360
Are you worried about me, Your Highness?

91
00:06:11,000 --> 00:06:13,759
You're still useful to me.

92
00:06:14,319 --> 00:06:15,560
If you were to die

93
00:06:16,199 --> 00:06:18,800
wouldn't my blood
have been shed for nothing?

94
00:06:21,879 --> 00:06:23,079
I see.

95
00:06:27,319 --> 00:06:28,879
What we have is just a transaction.

96
00:06:29,639 --> 00:06:31,240
You don't have to risk your life for me.

97
00:06:33,160 --> 00:06:34,199
I understand

98
00:06:34,839 --> 00:06:38,240
what's between us is a transaction.

99
00:06:41,079 --> 00:06:42,040
Now that you're awake

100
00:06:42,040 --> 00:06:43,120
rest well.

101
00:06:44,720 --> 00:06:45,639
As for the assassin

102
00:06:46,000 --> 00:06:46,959
I'll handle it.

103
00:06:49,160 --> 00:06:49,959
Your Highness.

104
00:06:53,079 --> 00:06:56,199
Please spare that assassin's life.

105
00:07:03,480 --> 00:07:04,920
So you took that blade for me

106
00:07:06,040 --> 00:07:07,279
just for his sake?

107
00:07:24,700 --> 00:07:26,660
ظآزMoonlight spills like quiet tidesظآز

108
00:07:26,910 --> 00:07:29,880
ظآزA celestial bird
brushes the mountain's edgeظآز

109
00:07:31,740 --> 00:07:33,220
ظآزWings of light drift through the airظآز

110
00:07:33,220 --> 00:07:36,900
ظآزLike blossoms that refuse to fadeظآز

111
00:07:37,680 --> 00:07:40,700
ظآزIt asks no right or wrongظآز

112
00:07:40,940 --> 00:07:43,700
ظآزNor fears the turning of fateظآز

113
00:07:44,820 --> 00:07:46,420
ظآزA trace of spring on the windظآز

114
00:07:46,500 --> 00:07:49,060
ظآزA whisper of a broken heartظآز

115
00:07:50,940 --> 00:07:53,020
ظآزA farewell song unfoldsظآز

116
00:07:53,300 --> 00:07:56,220
ظآزCarrying every sorrow within itظآز

117
00:07:56,620 --> 00:07:58,660
ظآزKarma weaves its endless threadظآز

118
00:07:58,780 --> 00:08:02,620
ظآزAnd I would follow you
without turning backظآز

119
00:08:03,100 --> 00:08:06,100
ظآزLife and death become
nothing sharp or finalظآز

120
00:08:06,420 --> 00:08:09,500
ظآزLove and hate are carried away
on the breezeظآز

121
00:08:10,100 --> 00:08:12,300
ظآزBefore freedom is ever reachedظآز

122
00:08:12,300 --> 00:08:15,340
ظآزOne must first dissolve into tearsظآز

123
00:08:15,940 --> 00:08:19,020
ظآزLove crosses every cycle
of life and deathظآز

124
00:08:19,220 --> 00:08:22,340
ظآزSo let me fall with youظآز

125
00:08:22,540 --> 00:08:25,480
ظآزAll the noise of the mortal worldظآز

126
00:08:25,580 --> 00:08:28,540
ظآزIs nothing compared to her eyesظآز

127
00:08:29,140 --> 00:08:32,460
ظآزWhoever said love itself is sinظآز

128
00:08:32,460 --> 00:08:36,100
ظآزWhen a heartbeat turns into
wind and moonlightظآز

129
00:08:36,100 --> 00:08:38,780
ظآزPainting a banquet
of endless spring bloomsظآز

130
00:08:39,500 --> 00:08:41,740
ظآزHow beautifulظآز

131
00:08:42,860 --> 00:08:46,100
ظآزTwo hearts leaning into one anotherظآز

132
00:08:47,660 --> 00:08:49,620
ظآزPerfectly, impossibly rightظآز
